  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Mentorship Award: Cultural &amp; Artistic Responses to Environmental Change (2021)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">12 individuals received a Mentorship Award Cultural and Artistic Responses to Environmental Change. This mentorship programme was implemented in collaboration with the Goethe Institute, and built on the learnings from the three joint calls for proposals on the same theme issued between 2018 and 2020. Through the programme, Prince Claus Mentorship Awards were granted to potential leaders active at the cross section between arts and culture and environmentalism. All work supported through this mentorship therefore contributes to Sustainable Development Goal 13: Climate Action, while specific projects address themes connected to more SDGs.</narrative>
  </description>
